[[File:Star_Wars_RPG_Combat_Jumpsuit.jpg|thumb|An illustration of a combat jumpsuit.]]
The '''combat jumpsuit''' was a heavily padded [[Jumpsuit/Legends|jumpsuit]] that provided limited protection against both physical and energy attacks. Weighing only eight [[Kilogram/Legends|kilograms]], it was designed with maximum flexibility in mind and did not restrict the wearer's movement considerably. The cost of a standard combat jumpsuit was 1,500 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]].<ref name="RPG-Core">''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game Core Rulebook]]''</ref> Later, the [[Tuff1 Combat Jumpsuit]] would be developed, using this type of suit as an example.

